node.text: Don’t forget! The @purinaone_us Petfinder Foundation drive is still happening until 8/31/21! During this time, Purina ONE will donate $1 to help adoptable pets find their forever homes (up to $28,000) for every person who signs up for the 28-day challenge. This hits very close to my heart, as my best bud Asher was a rescue who was in critical condition when I adopted him. I know not everyone is in the ideal situation to adopt more dogs, but this gives you the perfect opportunity to help these animals find their homes without having to add more animals to your pack! Click the link in my bio to learn more! #ad #veterinarian #adopt #vettech #veterinarymedicine #veterinarystudent
